<center><h2>Travel Tips</h2></center>
<center><ul >
	<li>Pack Light</li>
	<li>Try local food but be mindful of hygiene</li>
	<li>Stay Hydrated</li>
	<li>Keep Your documents safe</li>
	<li>Inform someone about your travel plans</li>
</ul></center>

